  "title": "Structure of TCR and antigen complexes at an immunodominant CTL epitope in HIV-1 infection.",
  "journal": "Scientific reports",
  "year": 2013,
  "authors": "Shimizu A, Kawana-Tachikawa A, Yamagata A, Han C, Zhu D, Sato Y, Nakamura H, Koibuchi T, Carlson J, Martin E, Brumme CJ, Shi Y, Gao GF, Brumme ZL, Fukai S, Iwamoto A."
